                        <h2>Pricing Reality</h2>
                        <p>The pricing difference between Lemlist and Instantly is significant and often misunderstood. Instantly charges a flat monthly rate regardless of team size — one price covers unlimited users. Lemlist charges per user, which means costs scale linearly with team size.</p>
                        <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
