                                    <tr><td>3 SDRs</td><td>$297/mo</td><td>$97/mo</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>5 SDRs</td><td>$495/mo</td><td>$97/mo</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>10 SDRs</td><td>$990/mo</td><td>$97/mo</td></tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <p>The math is clear: Lemlist is cost-competitive only for solo operators or very small teams. For teams of 3 or more, Instantly's flat pricing is dramatically cheaper. The question is whether Lemlist's personalization features justify the premium — and for many teams, they do, because higher reply rates mean fewer prospects needed to hit the same pipeline target.</p>
